        <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-2">{:trans; Everything You Need :}</h2>
        <p class="text-body-secondary mx-auto mb-0">
            {:trans; Production-ready foundations so you can focus on building your product, not boilerplate. :}
        </p>
